subSubSection.paragraph:
When preserved (Fig. 
2
), body pale. Prominent black blotches or spots on forehead and dorsal fin consistent with fresh condition. Forehead and dorsal-fin base dusky. Few faint dusky lines along, above and below lateral line. Edge of anal fin black.

